(1, 1, 'ROAST8RY : Roasting factory', '257/87 Suthep road, Suthep, Muang, Chiang Mai 50200', 'by appointments only', '+66 95 530 5360', 'info@roast8ry.com', 'roast8ry_', 'roast8ry', '4.6', 268, 'https://www.google.co.th/webhp?sourceid=chrome-instant&ion=1&espv=2&ie=UTF-8#q=coffee+chiang+mai&rflfq=1&rlha=0&rllag=18798428,98968402,416&tbm=lcl&tbs=lf_msr:-1,lf:1,lf_ui:9&rlfi=hd:;si:9712052777449963792', '4.5', 682, 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/Restaurant_Review-g293917-d3354946-Reviews-Ristr8to_Coffee-Chiang_Mai.html', 'This Roasting factory is our main coffee roasting lab where we will focus on how to develope the best flavor\r\nfrom each coffee using all knowledge we has learnt about different varietals and different processes of coffee\r\nfrom different farms around the world combined with our long experience in World Coffee Competitions.\r\nFor over 10 years that we have been obsessed with great coffee, to find highest quality green bean\r\nand develope our roasting profile to maximise the flavor in those coffee to provide\r\nthe best roasted coffee beans we can at the time to our customer.', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d15107.89292495012!2d98.97095837215905!3d18.799346265551033!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x86c8248b5fc04110!2sRistr8to+-+Specialty+coffee!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sth!4v1472224780766'),
(2, 1, 'ROAST8RY : LAB', '14 Nimmanhaemin road Soi 3, Suthep, Muang, Chiang Mai 50200', 'everyday : 8:00 - 17:30', '+66 95 530 5360', 'info@roast8ry.com', 'roast8ry_', 'roast8ry', '4.0', 1, 'https://www.google.co.th/search?q=doppio+ristr8to&ie=utf-8&oe=utf-8&client=firefox-b&gws_rd=cr&ei=dB_ZV86-DMrN0gT26a-ACg#q=doppio%20ristr8to&tbs=lf_msr:-1,lf:1,lf_ui:9&rflfq=1&rlha=0&rllag=18802542,98992621,2709&tbm=lcl&rldimm=2950688816710887106', '0.0', 0, '', 'Roast8ry Lab idea started in May 2015 and since then we have been continuously developing the concept\r\nmenu adding new knowledge and drinks we have learnt and created each year. At this LAB we have\r\nconcentrated our experience in World Latte art, World coffee in good spirits, and world Barista championship,\r\nthen turned them into intelligible menu for everyone. We have separated our menu into 5 different levels so our\r\ncustomer can easily choose the drinks that suit them depended on how well they know or would like to know\r\nabout coffee.', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d15107.185350762295!2d99.0060866!3d18.8072275!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x479daf5a0a43e38!2zQ2VudHJhbEZlc3RpdmFsIENoaWFuZ21haSDguYDguIvguYfguJnguJfguKPguLHguKXguYDguJ_guKrguJXguLTguKfguLHguKUg4LmA4LiK4Li14Lii4LiH4LmD4Lir4Lih4LmI!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sth!4v1472226516439'),
(3, 1, 'ROAST8RY : Flagship store', '24/9 Nimmanhaemin road Soi 17, Suthep, Muang, Chiang Mai 50200', 'opening in 2021', '+66 95 530 5360', 'info@roast8ry.com', 'roast8ry_', 'roast8ry', '0.0', 0, '', '0.0', 0, '', 'Roast8ry Flagship store is the beginning of our new level of coffee shops with unique concept that we would\r\nlike it to be the highend coffee destination of the world in every single detail.\r\nPlease stay tune for the coming.', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d1888.4906377006798!2d98.96787918351926!3d18.798987793840283!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x30da3a6207833303%3A0x34f9536bf99b37e!2sRistr8to+Lab!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sth!4v1472226693207'),
(4, 1, 'Doppio', 'Thapae Rd, Chang Moi, Mueang, Chiang Mai 50300', 'everyday : 7:08 - 19:00', '+66 98 549 4662', 'info@roast8ry.com', 'roast8ry_', 'roast8ry', '0.0', 0, '', '0.0', 0, '', 'Doppio is our 2nd coffee shop in Chiang Mai. Our concept is to share our knowledge to coffee beginner and\r\nlocal people who are not commonly drinking coffee in Chiang Mai, so we made this cult-concept cafe less\r\ncomplicated than our original Ristr8toand easier to understand for everyone. We would like to persuade\r\ncommon people to appreciate about good coffee, that is why we make our concept and our unique menu to\r\nget connected with normal people who are not coffee geek, so they can know more information about coffee,\r\nand enjoy coffee industry more.', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d1888.4906377006798!2d98.96787918351926!3d18.798987793840283!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x30da3a6207833303%3A0x34f9536bf99b37e!2sRistr8to+Lab!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sth!4v1472226693207');

