(4, 1, 'SK8LL COLLECTION', 'released date : 18/01/16', 'Released 3 new designs every year (and stop producing 3 of the oldest designs every year). Our T-shirt designs are inspired from many great coffee cities we have been to during our persuit of the perfect cup of coffee each year. If you would like to know which city are your favourite design inspirated from please ask our owner when he is in the house.', 'S;M;L;XL', 488, 4, 1, 1),
(5, 1, 'SK8LL COLLECTION', 'released date : 18/01/16', 'Released 3 new designs every year (and stop producing 3 of the oldest designs every year). Our T-shirt designs are inspired from many great coffee cities we have been to during our persuit of the perfect cup of coffee each year. If you would like to know which city are your favourite design inspirated from please ask our owner when he is in the house.', 'S;M;L;XL', 488, 5, 1, 0),
(6, 1, 'SK8LL COLLECTION', 'released date : 18/01/16', 'Released 3 new designs every year (and stop producing 3 of the oldest designs every year). Our T-shirt designs are inspired from many great coffee cities we have been to during our persuit of the perfect cup of coffee each year. If you would like to know which city are your favourite design inspirated from please ask our owner when he is in the house.', 'S;M;L;XL', 488, 6, 1, 0),
(7, 1, 'BLVK COLLECTION ', 'released date : 25/02/17', 'Released 3 new designs every year (and stop producing 3 of the oldest designs every year). Our T-shirt designs are inspired from many great coffee cities we have been to during our persuit of the perfect cup of coffee each year. If you would like to know which city are your favourite design inspirated from please ask our owner when he is in the house.', 'S;M;L;XL', 488, 7, 1, 0),
