(10, 1, 'SK8 COLLECTION', 'released date : 01/04/15', 'Released 3 new designs every year (and stop producing 3 of the oldest designs every year). Our T-shirt designs are inspired from many great coffee cities we have been to during our persuit of the perfect cup of coffee each year. If you would like to know which city are your favourite design inspirated from please ask our owner when he is in the house.', 'S;M;L;XL', 488, 10, 1, 0),
(11, 1, 'SK8 COLLECTION', 'released date : 01/04/15', 'Released 3 new designs every year (and stop producing 3 of the oldest designs every year). Our T-shirt designs are inspired from many great coffee cities we have been to during our persuit of the perfect cup of coffee each year. If you would like to know which city are your favourite design inspirated from please ask our owner when he is in the house.', 'S;M;L;XL', 488, 11, 1, 0),
(12, 1, 'SK8 COLLECTION', 'released date : 01/04/15', 'Released 3 new designs every year (and stop producing 3 of the oldest designs every year). Our T-shirt designs are inspired from many great coffee cities we have been to during our persuit of the perfect cup of coffee each year. If you would like to know which city are your favourite design inspirated from please ask our owner when he is in the house.', 'S;M;L;XL', 488, 12, 1, 0),
(13, 2, 'RISTR8TO PANTS', '', 'Our shorts and pants are released less often than our T-shirts, uncertainly depend on our owner creative mood. Again the designs came from our inspiration from different coffee cities we have been to around the world.', 'M (30 -32);L (34-36)', 880, 13, 1, 0),
(14, 2, 'RISTR8TO PANTS', '', 'Our shorts and pants are released less often than our T-shirts, uncertainly depend on our owner creative mood. Again the designs came from our inspiration from different coffee cities we have been to around the world.', 'M (30 -32);L (34-36)', 880, 14, 1, 0),
(15, 2, 'SK8LL COLLECTION', 'released date : 18/01/16', 'Our shorts and pants are released less often than our T-shirts, uncertainly depend on our owner creative mood. Again the designs came from our inspiration from different coffee cities we have been to around the world.', 'M (30 -32);L (34-36)', 880, 15, 1, 1),
(16, 2, 'SK8 COLLECTION', 'released date : 01/04/15', 'Our shorts and pants are released less often than our T-shirts, uncertainly depend on our owner creative mood. Again the designs came from our inspiration from different coffee cities we have been to around the world.', 'M (30 -32);L (34-36)', 880, 16, 1, 0),
(17, 2, 'SK8 COLLECTION', 'released date : 01/04/15', 'Our shorts and pants are released less often than our T-shirts, uncertainly depend on our owner creative mood. Again the designs came from our inspiration from different coffee cities we have been to around the world.', 'M (30 -32);L (34-36)', 880, 17, 1, 0),
(18, 2, 'SK8 COLLECTION', 'released date : 01/04/15', 'Our shorts and pants are released less often than our T-shirts, uncertainly depend on our owner creative mood. Again the designs came from our inspiration from different coffee cities we have been to around the world.', 'M (30 -32);L (34-36)', 880, 18, 1, 0),
(19, 2, 'SK8 COLLECTION', 'released date : 01/04/15', 'Our shorts and pants are released less often than our T-shirts, uncertainly depend on our owner creative mood. Again the designs came from our inspiration from different coffee cities we have been to around the world.', 'M (30 -32);L (34-36)', 880, 19, 1, 0),
(20, 3, 'Nikka glass', 'Capacity:200 ml.', 'This skull glasses are our favourite among those glasses we have found along our way of finding the cups and glasses for our signature menu and have been used it for many of our signature menus including our most selling Nikka Macchiato which become the name of this glass.', '', 680, 20, 1, 1),
(21, 3, 'Flat White cup', 'Flat white is a coffee beverage developed in New Zealand and Australia in the 1980s and was exported around the world in the 2010s. In Thailand, we dare to say that Ristr8to in one of the very first coffee shop to bring the Flat White to public. The shape and the size of this cup is really good for making great milk coffee drink with latte art.', 'Capacity:190ml', '', 380, 21, 1, 0),
(22, 3, 'Satan glass', 'Capacity:150ml', 'Another skull glass for our first signature drink: Ficardie which is inspired by our experience of Magic in Melbourne and Gibraltar in San Francisco.', '', 580, 22, 1, 0),
(23, 3, 'Cigar8to cup', 'Capacity:118ml', 'The Cigar8to is our Barista favourite drink. Our custom-made 4oz cup are designed for the perfect amount of milk and double shot of ristretto resulting in the balance rich flavor in the designed shape that will keep that whole round flavor from the first sip until the last sip.', '', 280, 23, 1, 0),
(24, 3, 'Ristr8to thermos bottle', 'Capacity:420ml', 'Keep your drink hot or cool for up the 8 hours. This thermos is fashionable bottle that are real practical and can be used in your daily life.', '', 488, 24, 1, 0),
(25, 4, 'Book I ', 'Specialty coffee guide', 'This book is for everyone who likes to drink, talk, and learn about coffe. Its content is comprehensive basic knowledge about coffee you would need to know in order to be more appreciated with your cup of coffee.', '', 280, 25, 1, 1),
(26, 4, 'Book II', 'Brewing Guild', 'This book is for everyone who likes to make coffee for yourself at home or begining Barista who are going to put their legs into the world of making one of the most complex drink on earth including how to buy coffee beans, how to buy coffee equipment, how to grind your coffee beans, recipes for more than 10 methods of making coffee, introduction of 8 great coffee origins, and more.', '', 340, 26, 1, 0),
(27, 4, 'Ristr8to : Note book set', '', '3 designs note book are our first merchandise ever released. We sell them as a set of 3 as your choice of designs.', '', 108, 27, 1, 0),
(28, 4, 'Ristr8to menu', '', 'We have always changed and updated our menu from our experience in coffee scene from many of the worlds great cities along our pursuit of the perfect coffee journey and we still have some of our previous menus for you to purchase them back home for the retro memory of Ristr8to.', '', 180, 28, 1, 0);

